For this, we will be using
the official test data

00:06:45.340 --> 00:06:46.980
from the theme unit test.

00:06:48.200 --> 00:06:51.740
So one of the things that I like
about spinning up test sites

00:06:51.740 --> 00:06:57.080
when comparing different themes is
that I get a much better comparison

00:06:57.080 --> 00:06:58.680
of apples to apples.

00:06:58.680 --> 00:07:02.430
If I try and actually look at
some of their example demos,

00:07:02.430 --> 00:07:07.170
things are just so customized and
so different between the demos,

00:07:07.170 --> 00:07:10.400
I can not really get a
