00:07:10.400 --> 00:07:14.290
what is being done by the
theme versus what is being done

00:07:14.290 --> 00:07:17.520
by the content and the
choices that have been made.

00:07:20.680 --> 00:07:24.550
So the Accessibility
Ready Tag; This is the tag

00:07:24.550 --> 00:07:30.390
in the WordPress repository,
and it means it covers some content.

00:07:32.970 --> 00:07:34.710
So we are going to go off

00:07:34.711 --> 00:07:38.120
to the actual WordPress
repository information.

