talk about quickly is classes.

00:48:00.570 --> 00:48:02.873
When you use classes
on your elements,

00:48:02.874 --> 00:48:04.880
it makes it very future-friendly.

00:48:04.880 --> 00:48:09.780
For example, adding screen reader
text, white text, large text,

00:48:09.780 --> 00:48:13.870
this allows you to later
update that large text globally

00:48:13.870 --> 00:48:17.090
by just changing the CSS and
not having to go into each

00:48:17.090 --> 00:48:18.580
and every page and make updates.

00:48:20.840 --> 00:48:25.050
And also adding a lot of things
like margins and paddings

00:48:25.050 --> 00:48:28.340
and having these as quickly
accessible CSS classes

00:48:28.340 --> 00:48:30.434
so that you can make
really easy tweaks

00:48:30.435 --> 00:48:32.110
when you are building up pages.

